00:15:55.361 --> 00:15:58.117
un mir Shavler zaynen geforn in Kovne opnemen.

00:15:58.663 --> 00:16:03.129
un a briv iz geven, fun vemen dos geyt di hilf.

00:16:03.861 --> 00:16:06.977
hob ikh ibergeleyent dem briv, un loyt dem adres

00:16:07.101 --> 00:16:10.419
hob ikh geshribn a bite briv in daytsh,

00:16:10.999 --> 00:16:14.857
m- a- az aza un aza zakh, az m'darf makhn

00:16:14.863 --> 00:16:20.122
a hiftn-knokhn IMPLANTATION operatsye,

00:16:20.348 --> 00:16:22.654
un ikh hob gekrogn a entfer,

00:16:23.098 --> 00:16:26.647
fun, nit fun zey vu ikh hob ge- vu ikh hob gebetn,

00:16:26.647 --> 00:16:32.306
nor f- m'hot dos durkhn televizye un durkhn radyo gezogt,

00:16:32.329 --> 00:16:37.874
un es hot zikh opgerufn eyner a froy, z- zi iz aleyn a dokter,

00:16:37.932 --> 00:16:40.525
der briv irer hob ikh nokh biz haynt.

00:16:40.598 --> 00:16:43.109
vi zi shraybt, ir vet zikh gevis bavundern

00:16:43.109 --> 00:16:48.272
az ikh a umbakante froy, ikh bin aleyn a yunge dokotorin, ikh bin nit keyn ortoped,

00:16:48.272 --> 00:16:55.959
ober ikh hob ikh hob kleyne a kleynem stazh, b- kleyne praktike, ober ikh hob a groysn viln aykh tsu helfn.

00:16:55.959 --> 00:17:00.068
un zi hot ongehoybn zukhn SPONSORn,

00:17:00.068 --> 00:17:04.911
velkhe zoln in dem hinzikht arayn helfn.

00:17:04.911 --> 00:17:13.127
un zi hot gefunen a a ortopedishe klinike in Keln, velkhe hobn zikh ongenumen

00:17:14.213 --> 00:17:17.818
o- o- ongenumen umzist makhn di operatsye.

00:17:18.415 --> 00:17:24.714
nu, un nakher hot zi geshafn gelt oyfn oyf di biletn hi- hin un tsurik,

00:17:24.714 --> 00:17:27.423
un tsum shlus hobn z- hot zikh geshe-

00:17:27.423 --> 00:17:32.713
ongerufn vayle dos hot er hot hot gemakht dortn a aza intervyu,

00:17:32.713 --> 00:17:35.430
un in bay dortn in klinike gufe,

00:17:35.430 --> 00:17:40.535
un in tsaytung, in Kelner Antsuger Shtats-Tsaytung,

00:17:40.535 --> 00:17:46.792
un es hobn zikh opgerufn di Luft- Lufthanza,

00:17:46.866 --> 00:17:56.664
un zey hobn umzist gemakht di veg mitn mitn luft- a luft-flug, ershte klas.

00:17:56.772 --> 00:18:01.426
un umetum, fun Keln zaynen mir gefloygn biz Frankfurt,

00:18:01.426 --> 00:18:04.227
dortn hot undz ervart glaykh a ROLLWAGEN,

00:18:04.227 --> 00:18:08.657
un m'hot undz arayngezetst in a tsveytn SAMOLYOT, in a tsveytn luft-tsug,

00:18:08.657 --> 00:18:16.897
un un fun dortn zaynen mir gekumen in Vilne, un in Vilne hot oykh oyf undz gevart. azoy organizirt iz geven di zakh. oyf tsurik, ya.

00:18:14.592 --> 00:18:15.953
dos iz shoyn oyf tsurik.

00:18:17.477 --> 00:18:22.145
ikh bin zeyer dank di mentshn, di familye Herhaus fun Keln,

00:18:29.914 --> 00:18:34.751
velkhe lebn in Keln, bin ikh zeyer dankbar,

00:18:34.858 --> 00:18:43.222
di dem adres gedenk ikh nit oyf oysveynik,

00:18:45.793 --> 00:18:55.760
aha! Markt Strase zeks. Doktor Herhaus Barbara. Markt Strase zeks,

00:18:57.454 --> 00:19:05.408
un ikh volt veln az m'zol ir efntlekh dortn, nu, opgebn koved,

00:19:05.408 --> 00:19:09.294
in Daytshland, oyber men ken dos makhn, aza mentsh.

00:19:10.009 --> 00:19:13.175
un zi iz shoyn do o bay undz oykh geven gekumen,

00:19:13.722 --> 00:19:16.129
zi hot gezogt, ikh muz zen vi ir lebt.

00:19:17.350 --> 00:19:22.491
ye, zogt mir itster, vi s'iz ayer zun hot er bakumen bildung?

00:19:22.750 --> 00:19:26.375
mayn zun iz a lerer, er hot geendikt dem institut do in Shavl.

00:19:26.277 --> 00:19:28.431
iz v- vi iz der nomen fun ayer zun?

00:19:26.375 --> 00:19:27.401
pedagog.

00:19:28.555 --> 00:19:29.679
Simon.

00:19:29.432 --> 00:19:30.843
Simon, ya.

00:19:30.158 --> 00:19:30.911
ya.

00:19:31.153 --> 00:19:32.632
dos iz loytn tatn?

00:19:31.356 --> 00:19:31.974
Simon.

00:19:32.402 --> 00:19:35.973
loyt mayn foter olevasholem. Simon, ye.

00:19:35.760 --> 00:19:37.239
un itster vu lebt er?

00:19:37.600 --> 00:19:40.024
itster lebt er Daytshland, in Hamburg.

00:19:39.962 --> 00:19:41.103
un vos tut er?

00:19:40.755 --> 00:19:43.384
er geyt durkh itster a kurs

00:19:43.384 --> 00:19:47.770
er lernt zikh, er er darf zikh iberkvalifitsirn.

00:19:48.096 --> 00:19:50.202
un nakher vet zayn baruf kursn,

00:19:50.202 --> 00:19:53.456
itster lernt er zikh di shprakh grintlekh.

00:19:54.762 --> 00:19:56.781
un er vet shoyn blaybn in Daytshland?

00:19:56.652 --> 00:19:58.114
kentik az ye.

00:19:57.934 --> 00:20:01.117
un vos iz er geven far a fakh far a lerer? vos hot er gele-

00:20:00.280 --> 00:20:03.801
fun di onfang-shuln, a lerer fun di onfang-shuln, un muzik.

00:20:03.992 --> 00:20:05.943
ot zet ir hot er geendikt di shule.

00:20:08.548 --> 00:20:10.567
ir klaybt zikh tsu forn tsu ayer zun?

00:20:10.759 --> 00:20:16.186
di tsayt vet vayzn. dertsu darf men den derlebn, ikh bin zeyer nit gezunt, bay mir iz do

00:20:16.345 --> 00:20:24.028
nirn-shteyner, koralishe, velkhe ikh veys nit vu un vi m'ken mir helfn.

00:20:24.028 --> 00:20:35.444
nor ikh volt zayn zeyer tsufridn az ir dort in Amerike volt zikh araynleygn in dem inyen un gebn mir hilf oyf vifl s'iz meglekh, ikh veys nit di letste

00:20:35.444 --> 00:20:41.111
dergreykhungen fun meditsin, nor ikh volt veln az men zol zikh in dem farinteresirn.

00:20:41.877 --> 00:20:45.347
ikh vil nokh lebn, ikh vil nokh dervartn fun mayn kind gutes.

00:20:46.095 --> 00:20:49.560
gut ikh a dank aykh zeyer far a sheynem intervyu,

00:20:49.560 --> 00:20:53.137
un ikh vintsh aykh a sakh nakhes fun ayer mishpokhe.

00:20:52.660 --> 00:20:55.117
a dank, a dank Khaim.

00:20:53.137 --> 00:20:54.459
un gezunt.

00:21:08.607 --> 00:21:18.134
do oyfn foto zet ir fun Kelem di fayer-lesher komand- komande,

00:21:18.664 --> 00:21:23.479
vu mayn foter iz do oykh, gefint zikh oykh.

00:21:23.479 --> 00:21:29.542
oyfn in ershte rey mitn berdele, fun links.

00:21:30.375 --> 00:21:36.953
for di krig iz dos, forgekumen umgefer in nay- in fertsiktn yor. ya.

00:21:36.953 --> 00:21:41.439
un mayn foter Khaim Simen Yavne.

00:21:52.043 --> 00:21:56.070
heyst es do zet ir dem oyf dem oyf dem bild,

00:21:56.363 --> 00:22:04.423
di yidishe folkshul Tarbut, fun Kelem, for fun for di krig,

00:22:04.986 --> 00:22:12.095
un mayn bruder gefint zikh do, in drite rey, yo in drite rey, der driter fun links.

00:22:12.095 --> 00:22:19.627
un ikh shtey avekgeshtelt di letste fun links, mit a hele kleydele.

00:22:31.378 --> 00:22:35.189
aha. do zet ir oyf dem bild,

00:22:35.189 --> 00:22:44.099
a grupe fun undzer klas in Kelem, fun gimnazye, vu ikh hob zikh gelernt,

00:22:44.099 --> 00:22:53.715
un eyner fun di fun di, mit-shilerin, mit-shiler, hot undz geshosn.

00:22:53.772 --> 00:22:57.734
di ale yidishe kinder vos hobn gelernt tsuzamen un

00:22:57.734 --> 00:23:02.940
bikhlal hot er geshosn di yidn, er hot genumen anteyl in shisn yidn. er zitst, er zitst

00:23:02.940 --> 00:23:10.230
in di ershte rey, der ershter rey, der tsveyter fun rekhts.

00:23:09.938 --> 00:23:11.147
vi iz zayn nomen?

00:23:10.832 --> 00:23:13.475
zayn nomen iz Yokobaytes Nikoles.

00:23:18.291 --> 00:23:24.107
do oyf dem oyf dem bild, dos bin ikh, for di krig,

00:23:24.265 --> 00:23:29.101
Yavne Miryam, nakher Voronove Mariye,

00:23:29.445 --> 00:23:32.561
for di krig, ven ikh hob gelernt in gimnazyum.

00:23:36.128 --> 00:23:41.912
do oyf dem bild, zet ir di tsvey tekhter fun

00:23:41.912 --> 00:23:48.221
dem mentshn Ratshkauskes, velkhe hobn velkhe hobn mir

00:23:48.919 --> 00:23:54.805
geratevet, velkhe hobn genumen oyf zikh dem ershtn fayer, vi men zogt dos.

00:23:54.805 --> 00:23:59.847
dos iz Kristina un Yadviga Ratshkavskaytes.

00:23:59.871 --> 00:24:04.421
velkhe zaynen shoyn, oyf beyde muz zogn olevasholem.

00:24:05.878 --> 00:24:08.538
nu, un der UNK.

00:24:07.768 --> 00:24:08.606
UNK.

00:24:09.085 --> 00:24:14.220
do oyf dem bild zet ir eyne fun di reterin velkhe hobn mir geholfn zikh rateven,

00:24:14.220 --> 00:24:17.870
dos iz di froy Minkevetshinye Kotrina.

00:24:18.028 --> 00:24:26.426
iz fun tsuker fabrik velkhe hot undz geholfn organizirn dem antloyfn fun tsuker fabrik.

00:24:27.023 --> 00:24:32.973
in nu ven mir zaynen dortn geven internirt.

00:24:33.756 --> 00:24:34.813
UNK.

00:24:35.865 --> 00:24:37.141
UNK.

00:24:37.789 --> 00:24:43.689
do oyf dem bild zet ir dem galekh Pozhole, in Kozhey,

00:24:43.898 --> 00:24:48.026
velkher hot mir geholfn antloyfn fun turme.

00:24:48.538 --> 00:24:54.202
do lebn Shavl nit vayt gefint zikh dos di shtetele.

00:24:54.512 --> 00:24:59.281
dos shteyt er lebn zayn kirkhe, lebn zayn kloyster.

00:25:02.190 --> 00:25:03.264
UNK.

00:25:05.987 --> 00:25:08.343
do oyf dem bild zet ir mir,

00:25:09.075 --> 00:25:18.502
Yavne, Miryam, nokh di krig, do bin ikh nokh nit geven farheyrat, in Shavl.

00:25:21.900 --> 00:25:22.839
itster,

00:25:22.103 --> 00:25:22.856
ye.

00:25:23.385 --> 00:25:31.178
do oyf dem bild zet ir dem denkmol in vald, lebn Shukyan,

00:25:31.178 --> 00:25:35.583
vu mayne eltern zaynen ershosn un es gefint zikh der brider-keyver,

00:25:35.583 --> 00:25:41.421
un do zaynen oykh mekaber ge- gevorn dray rabonim. der Kelmer rov,

00:25:41.421 --> 00:25:46.475
der Taviger rov un der Shukyaner rov, tsvishn di ale mentshn do arum.

00:25:46.475 --> 00:25:49.412
fir hundert, finf hundert men- mentshn.

00:25:49.305 --> 00:25:50.834
ver shteyt do oyfn bild?

00:25:49.412 --> 00:25:51.791
do lign mayne, do oyfn bild

00:25:51.791 --> 00:25:58.850
shtey ikh, un eyner un tsvey mener velkhe zaynen gekumen fun Izrael. gevezene Shavler.

00:26:02.822 --> 00:26:09.127
do oyf dem bild zet ir dem dem di matseyve,

00:26:09.184 --> 00:26:12.733
vu es zaynen mekaber geven gevorn

00:26:12.733 --> 00:26:17.345
di zibn kinder velkhe zenen antlofn fun Zhagarer shkhite

00:26:17.385 --> 00:26:26.925
un velkheve zaynen geven gevorn aroysgegebn fun fun mentshn, i- litvisher, in Shukyan,

00:26:26.925 --> 00:26:37.309
un zey hot men dershosn, oysgeton naket, un dershosn, in dem tog ershter november in in fir un f- in fir un fertsiktn yor.

00:26:42.580 --> 00:26:43.806
UNK.

00:26:44.082 --> 00:26:48.193
do oyf dem bild zet ir mayn zun, Voronov Simon,

00:26:49.836 --> 00:26:52.142
ven er hot geendikt di muzik-shule.

00:26:52.215 --> 00:26:55.516
dos iz geven dan. in Shavl.

00:26:55.978 --> 00:26:57.102
un do zogt UNK.

00:26:57.058 --> 00:26:58.548
do oyf dem bild

00:26:58.548 --> 00:27:03.009
zet ir di doktershe fun Daytshland, fun shtot Keln,

00:27:03.015 --> 00:27:08.257
velkhe hot geholfn organizirn umzist di operatsye far mayn man,

00:27:08.280 --> 00:27:13.589
tsu implantirn a hifte- gelenk, hiftn-gelenk.

00:27:13.275 --> 00:27:14.183
vi iz ir nomen?

00:27:14.170 --> 00:27:17.606
ir nomen iz Barabara Herhaus,

00:27:17.983 --> 00:27:24.157
un der adres iz Markt Strase zeks.
